name: GroceryListManager
0:
”Alexa, open grocery items”
”Add item to my custom grocery list”
”help”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: grocery items
des: This skill allows users to add grocery items to a custom grocery list. Its core functionality is to take the grocery item voice inout and send that input to a mongoDB server.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
